117	/**
118	 * RedesignedWorkspace — composition route for the §11–§17 chrome.
119	 *
120	 * Mounted at `/redesign`. Reads from `useBimStore` (same data as the
121	 * legacy `Workspace.tsx`) so engineers can A/B compare the two surfaces
122	 * without forking state. The canvas slot reuses the existing `Viewport`
123	 * / `PlanCanvas` components — only the chrome (TopBar / LeftRail /
124	 * Inspector / StatusBar / ToolPalette) is new.
125	 *
126	 * Spec sections wired here: §7 modes (1–7), §8 layout grid, §11 TopBar,
127	 * §12 Project Browser, §13 Inspector, §16 Tool palette, §17 StatusBar.
128	 */
